@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qawkuf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.04 / ((v1 + 0.83 - v2 + 0.13) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.33)))
    v2 = (v2 * ((v0 + 0.85 * tmp + 0.44) / v2))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v0 + 0.10) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
